children.name: SELECT "catalogue_productattribute"."code", "catalogue_productattribute"."type" FROM "catalogue_productattribute" WHERE "catalogue_productattribute"."code" IN ('subkinds', 'available') ORDER BY "catalogue_productattribute"."code" ASC

SELECT 1 AS "a" FROM "catalogue_product" INNER JOIN "catalogue_productattributevalue" ON ("catalogue_product"."id" = "catalogue_productattributevalue"."product_id") INNER JOIN "catalogue_productattributevalue_value_multi_option" ON ("catalogue_productattributevalue"."id" = "catalogue_productattributevalue_value_multi_option"."productattributevalue_id") INNER JOIN "catalogue_attributeoption" ON ("catalogue_productattributevalue_value_multi_option"."attributeoption_id" = "catalogue_attributeoption"."id") INNER JOIN "catalogue_productattribute" ON ("catalogue_productattributevalue"."attribute_id" = "catalogue_productattribute"."id") INNER JOIN "catalogue_productattributevalue" T6 ON ("catalogue_product"."id" = T6."product_id") INNER JOIN "catalogue_productattribute" T7 ON (T6."attribute_id" = T7."id") WHERE ("catalogue_attributeoption"."option" = 'megalomane' AND "catalogue_productattribute"."code" = 'subkinds' AND T6."value_boolean" AND T7."code" = 'available') LIMIT 1

SELECT "catalogue_productattribute"."code", "catalogue_productattribute"."type" FROM "catalogue_productattribute" WHERE "catalogue_productattribute"."code" IN ('kind', 'hypothenusa', 'facets', 'subtitle', 'subkinds', 'available') ORDER BY "catalogue_productattribute"."code" ASC

SELECT 1 AS "a" FROM "catalogue_product" INNER JOIN "catalogue_productattributevalue" ON ("catalogue_product"."id" = "catalogue_productattributevalue"."product_id") INNER JOIN "catalogue_attributeoption" ON ("catalogue_productattributevalue"."value_option_id" = "catalogue_attributeoption"."id") INNER JOIN "catalogue_productattribute" ON ("catalogue_productattributevalue"."attribute_id" = "catalogue_productattribute"."id") INNER JOIN "catalogue_productattributevalue" T5 ON ("catalogue_product"."id" = T5."product_id") INNER JOIN "catalogue_productattribute" T6 ON (T5."attribute_id" = T6."id") INNER JOIN "catalogue_productattributevalue" T7 ON ("catalogue_product"."id" = T7."product_id") INNER JOIN "catalogue_productattribute" T8 ON (T7."attribute_id" = T8."id") INNER JOIN "catalogue_productattributevalue" T9 ON ("catalogue_product"."id" = T9."product_id") INNER JOIN "catalogue_productattribute" T10 ON (T9."attribute_id" = T10."id") INNER JOIN "catalogue_productattributevalue" T11 ON ("catalogue_product"."id" = T11."product_id") INNER JOIN "catalogue_productattributevalue_value_multi_option" ON (T11."id" = "catalogue_productattributevalue_value_multi_option"."productattributevalue_id") INNER JOIN "catalogue_attributeoption" T13 ON ("catalogue_productattributevalue_value_multi_option"."attributeoption_id" = T13."id") INNER JOIN "catalogue_productattribute" T14 ON (T11."attribute_id" = T14."id") INNER JOIN "catalogue_productattributevalue" T15 ON ("catalogue_product"."id" = T15."product_id") INNER JOIN "catalogue_productattribute" T16 ON (T15."attribute_id" = T16."id") WHERE ("catalogue_attributeoption"."option" = 'totalitarian' AND "catalogue_productattribute"."code" = 'kind' AND T5."value_float" = 1.25 AND T6."code" = 'hypothenusa' AND T7."value_integer" = 8 AND T8."code" = 'facets' AND T9."value_text" = 'superhenk' AND T10."code" = 'subtitle' AND T13."option" = 'megalomane' AND T14."code" = 'subkinds' AND NOT T15."value_boolean" AND T16."code" = 'available') LIMIT 1
